    "body": "Fixes #2093\r\n\r\nWe had this functionality and removed it then, but now we are reintroducing this feature in our application.\r\n\r\nTo implement this feature we have made the following changes:\r\n* Added pause/resume button beside the stop button to perform pause/resume action on the downloading zim file.\r\n* Handling pause/resume via fetch library. The Fetch library has this functionality to pause/resume the current download so we have used it to implement this feature.\r\n* Added instrumentation test case for testing the pause/resume functionality.\r\n\r\n**UI changes**\r\n\r\n| Pause State  | Resume State | Notififcation |\r\n| ------------- | ------------- | ------------- |\r\n| ![1690789044670](https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/0bf90d9c-f92d-4f0e-9842-1a05e96cd217) |  ![1690789048353](https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/75e2ced1-92d4-433b-8807-2e157b981e81) | ![1690789043736](https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/60e74b74-8a84-4229-90ef-990b49a3801a) |\r\n\r\n**Feature working**\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/25457d27-9029-463e-b184-16e68209950c\r\n\r\n\r\n",
